インタフェースの使用
org.interledger.codecs.Codec

  • Codecを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.

      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER GeneralizedTime.
      class  OerIA5StringCodec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER IA5String.
      class  OerLengthPrefixCodec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER Length prefix octets.
      class  OerOctetStringCodec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER OctetString.
      class  OerSequenceOfAddressCodec
      A sequence-of type is encoded as a quantity field followed by the encoding of each occurrence of the repeating field of the sequence-of type (zero or more).
      class  OerUint256Codec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 256-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
      class  OerUint32Codec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 32-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
      class  OerUint64Codec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 64-Bit unsigned integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
      class  OerUint8Codec
      An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 8-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
